21 speaker.
22 (3) One member of the governor's office, appointed by the governor.
23 (4) The secretary of the Department of Public Safety and Corrections or his
24 designee.
25 (5) The secretary of Louisiana Works or her designee.
26 (6) The executive director of the Louisiana Sheriffs' Association or his designee.
27 (7) The executive director of the Louisiana District Attorneys Association or his
28 designee.
29 (8) The president of the Louisiana District Judges Association or her designee.
