HR 273 Engrossed 2026 Regular Session Chance Henry
Creates a task force to study and make recommendations relative to the current
administration, efficacy, and statutory framework of work release programs administered
by the Dept. of Public Safety and Corrections (DPS&C) and to report its findings to the La.
House of Representatives no later than Feb. 1, 2027.
